<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614869' id='t-614869'>꼭 뛰어야 하나요?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617368' id='t-617368'>아니면 그냥 뇌에 산소를 공급해주는</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620034' id='t-620034'>에어로빅 운동을 하면 되는건가요?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621663' id='t-621663'>다른 운동이라도 격렬하면 상관없나요?</span>
